casebody.data:
LOUISIANA DELTA CATTLE CO., INC., v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 43575] [93 C. Cls. 662;

314 U. S. —]

Flood control; taking of property; consequential damages.

Decided May 5, 1941; petition dismissed.

Plaintiff’s petition for writ of certiorari denied by the Supreme Court October 13, 1941.
